data.description: Beautifully renovated home in country setting, but conveniently close to town!  This gorgeous open floor plan home has 3 beds/3 baths and has been updated throughout.  New roof, an updated kitchen, new paint, light fixtures, faucets and much more!  Master en suite boasts a jetted tub and separate shower, plus his and her closets.  A full size, walk out basement where finishing has began, but not been completed (a bathroom has been finished and drywall hung), doubles the square footage while also providing a ton of storage.  A deck overlooking this wooded lot provides the perfect spot to enjoy the large private backyard.  Two car garage and a 24X12 shed complete this beautiful package.
